<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَهُمْ ما يَشاؤُنَ فِيها وَلَدَيْنا مَزِيدٌ <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
