<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٥٨- وَالسَّماءِ ذاتِ الْبُرُوجِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَالْيَوْمِ الْمَوْعُودِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَشاهِدٍ وَمَشْهُودٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢٧-<span class="c5"> الازفة:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٥٩- وَأَنْذِرْهُمْ يَوْمَ الْآزِفَةِ إِذِ الْقُلُوبُ لَدَى الْحَناجِرِ كاظِمِينَ ما لِلظَّالِمِينَ مِنْ حَمِيمٍ وَلا شَفِيعٍ يُطاعُ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
